Hi Jenna,



There will be three changes to the existing courses towards Astat ( current=
 SFU course requirement document attached).



  1.  Need to replace STAT 341 with STAT 260/261 under Computer Skills. We =
changed the course code from 341 to 260/261. It is almost the same course o=
utline.  STAT 260 is the lecture portion and STAT 261 is the lab portion.( =
Outlines attached)
  2.  Need to add STAT 440 and STAT 452 under Stat Electives ( Outlines att=
ached). These are new courses.

Please feel free to contact me if you need any other information. Thanks ag=
ain.

Kind Regards,


Harsha Perera
Undergraduate Program Chair and Faculty Advisor
Department of Statistics and Actuarial Science
Simon Fraser University


