From: Jenna Sykes <Jenna.Sykes@unityhealth.to>
Sent: Tuesday, November 3, 2020 5:12:42 AM
To: Gamage Perera
Subject: RE: AStat Accredited Course list updated - SFU...

Hi Harsha,

Thank you for the email. To update the list of accredited courses, please e=
mail the courses in question to the Accreditation Committee (accreditation@=
ssc.ca<mailto:accreditation@ssc.ca>) or myself. If you could include the co=
urse code and a brief outline of the topics covered in the course, that wou=
ld be great. This will then be sent out to be reviewed by two reviewers on =
the Accreditation Committee to check that it meets the requirements listed =
on the website.

Hope this helps,

Jenna Sykes, M.Math, P.Stat
Research Biostatistician
Tel: 647-239-7923

